<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<bug>
    <id>13360</id>
    <title>Code generated by the  Get Code  link does not reflect the state of the  Show Header  checkbox</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Repro:</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.2">- Go to specified URL</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.3">- Uncheck the  Show Header  checkbox</sentence>
            <sentence id="1.4">- click  Get Code</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">The XFBML result is:
&amp;lt;fb:activity recommendations= true &amp;gt;&amp;lt;/fb:activity&amp;gt;</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">The iframe code is:
&amp;lt;iframe src= http://www.facebook.com/plugins/activity.php?site=www.example.com&amp;amp;width=300&amp;amp;height=300&amp;amp;header=true&amp;amp;colorscheme=light&amp;amp;recommendations=true  scrolling= no  frameborder= 0  style= border:none; overflow:hidden; width:300px; height:300px;  allowTransparency= true &amp;gt;&amp;lt;/iframe&amp;gt;</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">Note that the XFBML does not include the  header= false   and the iframe mistakenly includes  header= true .</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
